articles.title: Tina Turner Is the 10th Singer From ‘We Are the World’ All-Star Charity Single to Die - Billboard
articles.description: Turner was the first female voice listeners heard on the record, which raised millions to fight famine in Africa.
articles.content: Tina Turner accomplished so much in her 50-year career that her presence on the all-star charity single “We Are the World” didn’t get a lot of attention following her death on Wednesday at age 83. Bu… [+2770 chars]
